header: Test vectors of type JsonWebSignature are intended for tests that check the
verification operation of a JSON Web Signature library.

JsonSerialization.description: The JWE/JWS is encoded with JSON serialization instead of compact serialization.

ModifiedPadding.description: The PKCS #1 padding of the signature has been modified.

WrongPrimitive.description: The signature uses a different algorithm than the algorithm specified in the key.

AlgIsNone.description: Algorithm none must not be accepted by default.
